HOUSE BILL 2390
By Martin B
SENATE BILL 2313
By Stevens
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 7,
Chapter 82, Part 3, relative to utilities.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 7-82-307(a)(2)(D), is amended by
deleting the subdivision and substituting:
(D) This subdivision (a)(2) does not prohibit a commissioner from serving for
more than two (2) consecutive terms in counties having a population, according to the
2020 federal census or any subsequent census, of:
not less than nor more than
28,800 28,900
42,700 42,800
50,400 50,500
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
